{"tid":2450725,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"前港龍機師及組合Square 成員李傑志決定轉行　開速遞公司做運輸另謀出路","createTime":"2021-03-17T15:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T19:24:12.000Z","uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bc4bc97a416862c97b508ae8dba5519419f7c66d","tid":2450725,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:10:15.000Z","msg":"去年10月，因為國泰港龍航空大裁員兼重整業務而失業的高級副機師李傑志（Brian），其實在當副機師之前，曾在2008年以男子組合「Square」成員身份當歌手，不過組合在2011年解散，他亦在同年投考私人飛機牌和受訓，在2013年加入港龍當機師。<br />\n<br />\n故此，他早前參加TVB舉辦的《衝上雲霄大選》比賽，望藉此重返演藝圈，可惜他最終落敗。李傑志最近決定改行，與朋友合資開公司投身運輸業，他並在個人社交平台上載一張在清潔貨Van的照片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2903929/brianlee_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2903929%2Fbrianlee_600.jpg&h=fc05c6cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f49cee0e10071cd8f5fccdc9d0ed275b92dd7224","tid":2450725,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/s1080x1080/129410993_396213408154345_1623656940171894474_n.jpg?tp=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_ohc=KLvEiZ6hgxkAX8n_leD&amp;oh=64cb6c2654f25de2bb0d8376edf8b543&amp;oe=607CE41E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fv%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2Fs1080x1080%2F129410993_396213408154345_1623656940171894474_n.jpg%3Ftp%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lax3-1.cdninstagram.com%26_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_ohc%3DKLvEiZ6hgxkAX8n_leD%26oh%3D64cb6c2654f25de2bb0d8376edf8b543%26oe%3D607CE41E&h=49917d9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/s1080x1080/125775397_394059228559831_1715551181786239404_n.jpg?tp=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_ohc=flp2OWwWWDAAX8dIMTz&amp;oh=cee712bbbd7720838d6bdf050edb6cd3&amp;oe=607BCEBE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com%2Fv%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2Fs1080x1080%2F125775397_394059228559831_1715551181786239404_n.jpg%3Ftp%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lax3-2.cdninstagram.com%26_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_ohc%3Dflp2OWwWWDAAX8dIMTz%26oh%3Dcee712bbbd7720838d6bdf050edb6cd3%26oe%3D607BCEBE&h=91728f9c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e40d56819498fdf4c49d3b13b4205fd0d49252d7","tid":2450725,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:10:46.000Z","msg":"「大家好，我係前KA機頭Brian，同大家都係十月嗰時無得再飛......<br />\n<br />\n本著「細個唔讀書，大個做運輸」嘅精神，小弟同幾個師兄弟開左間叫龍仔速遞嘅小型速遞公司，希望搵兩餐之餘，仲可以保育翻龍仔個牌頭。<br />\n<br />\n龍仔主要做食材嘅運輸，係啱啱嘅新年，就幫三間餐廳送左幾百個盤菜，同近千底年糕，亦都有運凍肉、蛋糕等等，而嚟緊都會開始運埋寵物食糧。<br />\n<br />\n不過而家經濟差搵食艱難，希望大家可以支持下龍仔，等我地幫下大家做運輸。只要係ex-crew或者仲飛緊嘅同事，無論咩類型嘅網店，龍仔都使命必達，保證將件貨安全穩妥咁送俾個客。」"},{"pid":"8fb6cbfac0f04730ff7bff5e2ae48e8a960a0b51","tid":2450725,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:11:00.000Z","msg":"最後，他落力為公司宣傳稱：「如果大家可以俾個機會龍仔嘅，我地會用非冷凍車嘅價錢，用冷凍車幫大家做即日攞，即日送嘅速遞服務。若然唔需要凍車嘅，我地可以offer特惠嘅價錢俾大家。」<br />\n<br />\n李傑志更寫下手提電話，以便客人隨時查詢。最後以tag補充寫道：「#航空業自救經濟圈#細個唔讀書大個做運輸#龍仔速遞識飛咁濟」"},{"pid":"97a7d18c4f1804abfad0a3b3d65ddee750f9fc3a","tid":2450725,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:11:52.000Z","msg":"韓仔feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68aaa93ec6a6c95617958914505273b077ec0b3e","tid":2450725,"uid":84037,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:12:00.000Z","msg":"狗屎垃圾都post上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c631b9be12ec7b6d533ffbd179a9b94a7b9c3b","tid":2450725,"uid":160592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T15:14:06.000Z","msg":"都算無運"},{"pid":"5531d05ad1449028cd30752439f3467fde902c33","tid":2450725,"uid":53780,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-0